{
  "text": "A possible explanation is that hypothyroidism takes a number of years to evolve to a clinical requirement for thyroid hormone supplementation, which might then elicit progression of a pre-existing, indolent, subclinical cancer [CITATION_1] . This sequence is wholly speculative.",
